# Project Context — Website Audit Tool

Read `AGENTS.md` before making any changes. It is the authoritative source of truth.

## Hard Constraints

- **Single URL only** — no multi-page crawling, no sitemap traversal
- **Factual metrics and AI insights must be separated** — in the UI, in code structure, and in prompts
- **Every OpenAI call must be logged** — use `src/lib/logging/prompt-logger.ts`
- **Insights must cite extracted metric values** — no generic recommendations

## Architecture Boundaries

```
scraper/ → metrics/ → ai/ → logging/
```

- `src/lib/scraper/` and `src/lib/metrics/`: zero OpenAI imports
- `src/lib/ai/`: prompts + OpenAI call + Zod validation only
- Prompts live in `src/lib/ai/prompts/` — never inline in route handlers

## Shared Types

All Zod schemas and inferred types live in `src/types/`. Import from there across layers.

## Required Deliverables

- 8 factual metrics extracted and displayed separately from AI output
- `AuditInsights` covering: SEO, messaging, CTA, content depth, UX
- 3–5 prioritized recommendations with `metricRefs`
- Prompt logs at `docs/prompt-logs/`
